# Paths repo-roast's local scan (CLI / pre-commit hook) skips.
# Gitignore-lite: one path prefix per line; `#` starts a comment.
#
# repo-roast dog-foods its own scanners in the pre-commit hook, and a security
# scanner's rule sources and test fixtures necessarily contain the very
# patterns they detect. Exclude them so the self-scan doesn't flag itself.
src/lib/scanners
